// ProgressBar
// Determinate or indeterminate progress bar with color variants.
// Indeterminate mode uses a CSS keyframe animation for the sliding bar effect.

FUNCTION ProgressBar(props) -> ReactNode                                  EXPORT
  Renders a track div with a fill div inside.
  IF indeterminate, applies an animated sliding style; the value prop is ignored.
  IF determinate, sets the fill width to value% (clamped 0–100).
  Color variants (default/success/warning/error) map to Tailwind background colors.
